obvious.prefuse
Class PrefuseObviousTuple

java.lang.Object
  obvious.prefuse.PrefuseObviousTuple
All Implemented Interfaces:
obvious.data.Tuple
Direct Known Subclasses:
PrefuseObviousEdge, PrefuseObviousNode
public class PrefuseObviousTuple
extends Object
implements obvious.data.Tuple

Implementation of an Obvious Tuple based on Prefuse toolkit. Obvious and Prefuse tuples are pretty close, this class is mainly a wrapper.

Author:
Pierre-Luc Hemery
